HEADWORD: Hierarch
<hw>Hi"er*arch</hw> <pr>(h⟦imac⟧"⟦etil⟧r*⟦aum⟧rk`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[LL. <ets>hierarcha</ets>, Gr. <?/; <grk>"iero`s</grk> sacred (akin
